values:
so last i wrote i believe i was 16 - i say this jokingly because my birthday has passed. i was going to write in this at work but it slipped my mind- more than once. i dont really want to write about what i've been up to but i guess i should fill you in a little bit. 9 more days of hell and then the summer comes - the headliner in my car is bubbling down and it is bothering the shit out of me, i need to make a girls night soon, and i've shed some tears more frequently lately. no i'm not a baby- i just care too much. so anyway - i'll tell you about my day today. Its thursday and tho i did not realize it - a lot has happened today. this morning i woke up late and rushed around and i made enough time to grab a yogurt which is good because i perk up a little more with food. me steve and sara made our way to school and i had treacherous physical education first period. nobody in their right mind wants to play frisbee at 7:30 in the morning. but they make us anyway. in gym is when i usually have good chats and walk the track. anywhoo - so i went to chem with psycho loh and took a quiz that was a joke - yet she drops the bomb that we have a huge test on things i cant even pronounce - let alone memorize. school kills mee - so lunch was pretty gross considering i had to watch the half retarded freshman boy be provoked by the unbelievably sophmoric sophmore boys. (irony? i think not) anywhoo so this kid who i call beetlejuice because he reminds me of that guy ate about 9 packets of butter, creamcheese, ketchup and some other average condiments provided by jj's cafeteria. anyway so right at the end of the period this kid threw up and that was it- everybody ran- atleast he made some money off of it. the rest of the day wasnt too bad - tests and notes . the usual bullshit of school. after school i came home and ate and chatted with mommy - i havent been sleeping good because i've been pretty stressed out lately so i took a nap . chatted on the phone with ren for a while. went back to sleep then i had to force myself out of bed to go to work - ugh -- work sucked i spent an hour and a half reading and the rest working and pacing until i got to go home. so i drive home and i must say it was a very peaceful drive i listened to some blink and just mellowed out. so when i got home i had to throw on a wash, do some homework, take care of the dogs, clean my room, fold some laundry, get ready for bed, and fight with timmy and kev. SOMEWHERE in the midst of it all i got electricuted. and i felt high - although my hand has been spiratically spazzing i must say i feel a little strange *smiles* wow i got in a fight with t & k over towels. see i do all the laundry in my house (ash remember that surprise party when i was like "oh come do laundry with me?" hahahaa) yea so i hate doing all the towels that they use and waste - it just pisses me off .. they called me a towel nazi - i just lost it-- so i usually just update for ashley because she reads this and i love her for it. i need sleep now - love youuuu [ashley] mwah*

<3.maur-

5 days until my birthday- happy birthday to hanna!!! and my gammy RIP -- so i'm having an off day today.. and livejournal of course is the place to vent - haha mainly because people can choose to read it or dismiss it - idc as long as i get it out of my head. school wasnt too bad today its just that my fridays suck when i know i just have work that night. after school i decided to go for a walk with scruffman and sara because its been a long time since we've done that. me and sara have a peculier relationship. we have these massive fights that widdle away to an unspoken apology and we go right back to the way we were. we chatted about her prom tonight and how exciting and of course i complained to her because shes the only one that will really tell me to shut up and get my shit together when i need to hear it. i was supposed to pick up my lovely boyfriend today at 3:30 as usual and he called me at 2:40 to tell me to get him at 3 which was physically impossible for me to get ready to get him and make it there - i dont want to get into it but i ended up not getting him and i havent talked to him since and i want to kill somebody right now. so when he hung up on me i brought the garbage cans in for mommy and got dressed to run errands. i got a birthday card from my grandma obrien which is awesomee!! so i went to the bank and cashed it and went to nissan and finally ordered my new sun visors!!! i love ittt .. so they will be in on ...mmm tuesday? after that i drove down 9 and got through every light and i started to perk up . i went to miss sara's house to see how beautiful she looked for her boyfriend's prom and i must say - she should have worn that dress to jay's junior prom because it was sooooo pretty - sara if you read this anymore i loveee youu* barcia showed up too to take some pictures of me . just kidding - but she came to see sara. we all took pictures and laughed and then i had to be off to work *sad face* -- on my way to work i got sad again. i was stuck in traffic by the little playground by fishkill elementary and i was watching the little kids play. i saw this little girl with long brown hair on the swings and she had that little "i wouldnt want to be anywhere else right now" smile on. i remember when i used to go on the swings and swing as high as i could and jump as far as i could get and usually landed in the dirt but i had that same smile on my face. i really do miss when i was a little kid with not a worry in the world. i moved up about 10 feet and i was still watching- the girls mother came over and told her it was time to leave and she started to cry. her mom told her the swings will be there tomorrow- but that girl has no idea that in a couple tomorrows they won't be there - she wont be there. she'll be sitting in her car watching another little girl play and she'll reminiss like this - i hope whoever reads this can relate - or maybe i'm just talking randomly. comment if you love me* mwah-

<3.miss maura jean*

i'm very excited yet i'm not because i like being 16 ... 17 seems old and your supposed to mature ya know? - anywhoo so my weekend was not bad at all. saturday night renato got me and we went out to eat at pizza uno's - it was really busy because of mother's day and i saw dirty mexican works there . that was funny - the waitress was a bit eccentric and she was quite fond of my boyfriend... hahaa so we went back to his house and snuggled for a while - so sunday i was planning on hanging out with my mommy for a bit and hanging out with my love at night but i ended up having to go to yorktown to see the obrien's yet again - what funnn .. i slept on the couch and watched baseball with my cousins. i got home kind of late and i was pretty pooped. monday i had to work which blew but i had off tuesday and wednesday. tuesday i got out of school and got renato from work and we hung out for a while . we cleaned my car and he power washed under my hood which is completely frikin awesome of him because i'm so happyyy!! lol wednesday i left school early and went to the dentist with him . his car is still not ready which sucks - but he's getting it tomorrow .. supposedly - lol so todayy is nickyy's birthday so happyy birthdayyy to himmm!!! -- after school renato left work early because he hates bj's with a strong passion and we put my deck in - I FINALLY CAN LISTEN TO MY CDS!!!! im sucha happy clam and i absolutly love my boyfrienddd. but i feel bad because he does things he doesnt have to do and i would love him either way - hes my <3* "sucha kind young soul" as ashley would say - lol so by the time he was done it was 5 and i was supposed to be here...... woops - ahh well this 'job' is a joke so they dont care. now 3/4 speakers work - yayy .. wednesday is my birthday and i'm going to get money and such so i'm going to buy visors, speakers, and possibly some other things - im waiting for my new floor matts - yayy!! yea so i better get my toosh off to working on papers because im oh-so lazy today - and i will be back here tomorrow ughh -- loveyou's* mwahh-

<3.maurajeanie~

MY BIRTHDAY IS COMING!!! awesomeee . so last i wrote was freakin' april 25th so quite a lot has happened. for starters prom was the 29th - i went to the after party at nickyy's with renato but i suppose we went a little too early because everybody was-- well still sober and very quiet. i had a fun night with my lovely boyfriend tho - i heard nick's got crazy - anywhoo . so the next day i was home at 7:30AM because my mom insisted we leave at 8 to go to the wedding. oh no we didnt leave until like 9 or 10 - i slept a bit and rolled out of bed and got my shit in the car and went back to sleep. on the way down timmy got sick because he was very hungover from spring fling weekend and midway he decided to puke. he jumped out of the car and blechhh - we finally got to the hotel and saw pretty much the whole o'brien family. keep in mind i was unshowered- hungover- and still half asleep. so we went up to our rooms and i waited for my brothers to get ready and go walk around aimlessly so i could have my room to myself - showering was so nicee! hahaa - i got all pretty pretty and made my way to find the rest of the o'brien clan. we went to the wedding and it was so cute - i can't wait to get married . leigh was gorgeous!! it was crappy out tho so the day was kind of depressing. then we were off to the reception! good foodd . huge family . and by the end of the night - the majority of us were all drunk. kevin was ridiculous tho - he does NOT know when to stop. after the reception we went back to the hotel and we were all going to the bar - well my dad got lost beause pennsylvania is officially the worst state- ever. we eventually got back and i went into the bar - most of the underage boys got thrown out but they didnt say anything to mee! hahaa - thats probably because i was dressed up and looked dammnnn sexy - or just because i have boobies. who cares i got to stay - but i felt like absolute crap so i made my way out of the bar and up to the room to go to sleep- the next morning we said goodbye to everybody and we got lost- yet again- trying to find a diner. oh no god forbid these penn.people let us out of their state - so in the car everybody started fighting - thats a given now-a-days . and we got home - renato came and got me - he finally got his car back that friday!!! and we went to his house to hang out - school this past week sucked - i seriously count down the days until i have my weekend . pretty soon it will be summer and i'll miss it - seeing everybody everyday - then i'll be a senior and that sounds so crazyyy - anywhoo last night i worked and renato came to visit - we left and went to his house and fell asleep together. i feel bad i keep this kid up so late when he has work so bright and earlyy !! - hahaa so i'm at work right now. oh the 5th was me and renatos 8th month being together - thats sucha long time and it feels like its only a little bit !! i love itt - so i need to go finish some papers and homework and get out of here! talk to you's soon - leave a comment if you'd like - love yous*

love always mauRaJean !!

it's been a while ehh ? i miss writing in this thing - nobody uses livejournal anymore . anywhoo what have i been up to lately? well this weekend was a nice quiet little weekend for myself . i spent with my boyfriend of coursee hahaa - my paycheck for april is going to be a good one .. so i'm excited! prom is this friday WHICH i'm not going because i couldn't find a dress and its a big waste of money SO me and renato are going to nickyy's afterwards - which is goodd because i still get to see everybody . but who knows - school is a fucking joke - it seems like all my friends are COOL - no more comments because colleen and ashh know whats upp . love you girls* anywhoo so i have a plan for myself which i swear to god i'm going to try to stick to - since all fall winter and the better part of spring i've been nothing but a lazy little couch potato i decided that a couple mornings a week i'm going to wake up 15 minutes early and go for a run - i'm gonna do it! i was going to this morning but i woke up late and i had a fever all day and wanted to pass out and die and punch a few people in their heads . me and my mommy went tanning and let me give some advice - DONT GO TANNING IF YOU HAVE A FEVER - i almost passed out and i had to jump out of my little turbo cooker 4 minutes early. i was shaking . anyway this morning there was an assembly thing for drugs and alcohol and it was pretty sad . and i bet it put a guilt trip on everybody because they are drinking friday  - hahaa .. sOo after my tanning adventure i picked up renato from bj's because his car is STILL in the shop - i'm actually starting to miss it . we snuggled for a while then off to work for mee - i have to get gas soon and its definately over 2 weeks now . i've been saving gas because steve drives to school - i lovee itt . yeepp so if anybody still reads this feel free to comment - wish i could say alot more - maybe some heavy venting next time ? who knowss - haha love you guys mwah*

<3.maurajeanie*

so yea myspace is the shit but livejournal is a little more personal is it not? well i'm going to be stuck in 2004 with my lj and love it like i always have. hahaa - next month will be my one year anniversary of my being a part of the lj community and to celebrate... i'll try to write more often . hahaa - so anywhoo kiddies i'm updating now. i need to find a new job that pays more and i wont have to touch a paper that says jesus on it. no offense to him but i cant take this shit anymoree! - renato started work which sucks because i work at night and he works during the day so i dont see him as much . this is also a reason as to why i need a better job - anywhoo so my car... let me get started on that - i need to fix everything on it to perfection and i dont want my bank account to go below $2,000 because thats my emergency money . lol -- my birthday is coming so if you'd like to contribute to 'help maura's car' fund i'll be taking contributions anytime from now 'til then. just kidding - kind of ? --- yea anyway let me tell you what i've been up to lately . friday i had work and i locked myself out of my car - it was a rather long story that consists of me jumping up and down infront of the neighbors window, renato saved me and i got home a few minutes late. lol then i went to his house and we ate wendys and napped . saturday i went to my cousin's bridal shower and it was fun . it was my first one . they had the most amazing food and i was in heaven - when she opened up her presents i got garbage duty - i just had to pick up the paper so it wasnt bad . i'm excited for the wedding - too bad its the day after my prom which really sucks . speaking of which it is really pissing me off now- i'm going dress shopping tomorrow and hopefully i'll start feeling a little better about this.. anywhoo so when i got home from the shower renato picked me up . i bought him a pumpkin pie cuz we havent had one in forever and it was yummmyyy<3* we went to the mall a little later only to discover the galleria is on a very steep journey downhill - it sucked i really didnt see more than 2 things i actually liked . we went home and snuggled a bit and then i went home . sunday was a nice quiet little day . laid around with him again - when the warm weather comes were going to stop hibernating - i need to go tanning again but i'm just too lazy to go . ah well - so monday i had work and today i'm here yet again - i have off 'til saturday yayy!!! when i came home today my mom had her friends over for her little irish party and i ate with them because i loveee the food . hahahaa i went for a walk with sara and her sister too then i went to bj's to see my love . now im at work and i need to finish my homework . renato might come visit too . lol love you's mwah*

<3.maura'

sOo.. today we got let out early which is wonderful - except now i don't go to work so i don't make any money which sucks the big one. ahh well - i've been in a rough mood today so maybe it's best i stay hidden from the world. some heavy venting about to be exposed: this week i need to go prom dress shopping- i keep saying that but i never get a change to go. i need to clean my room too but thats also a lost cause -- my boyfriend picked at me about having old screen names that i don't use. i guess i go on late at night and talk to some boys or something because i'm that kind of girl riight?. fake, sneaky, and a liar is what i'm described as - and a hoe. AWESOME - it's good to know the person you care most about can act so cold all of a sudden > and i'm the asshole thats left laying in her own little discreet world wondering what happens next and the doubt only multiplies. so i need to do my homework and i've done abso-fuckin'-lutly nothing productive that i intended on doing today. i need to go far away somewhere nice and warm all by myself and i will be a happy little clam. i don't even know what to write right now . i'll have something better tomorrow hopefully - love you's* oh and here's a little something for whoever would like to fill this out -smiles- mwah*

at work once again - figures . so anywhoo i'm happy to say this week is over . no more projects or long homework assignments to do so my stress level is decreasing . i've been so tired lately though - i get dizzy if i stand for more that 3 minutes probably due to the lack of sleep. i wasn't on time for school more than one time this whole week - i think it was thursday that i came in 5th period . hahaa oh well - i would tell you what i've been doing but honestly i do not remember. i know i worked 4 nights this week and i made 140 dollars . hellyeaa - next week i'm working a bunch of times and march 2nd is me and renato's 5 monthh! excitingg!! -- softball is starting for the girls and me and my couch potato self will continue to vegitate . i'll come watch your games tho! hahaa - yea so yesterday was an interesting little friday . i came home from school and planned on going to kohnls, tanning, and work but was disrupted by a phonecall that spoiled my mood and i guess i got a little crazyy - oh well i'm better now . but im pissed off that i didn't get to go tanning because i'm ghostly white and it sucks when you have no more tanlines due to the fact that everythings faded. hahaa - oh well i'll go monday or something. this week won't be that bad i hope . i think tuesday me and amanda are going to go prom dress shopping yay! i don't even know if i'm going yet though - oh well if i find a dress i like i'm going - thats my theory. so yea i finished all my work and now i'm going to start my math homework - lucky mee . comment if you'd like to - so i still know who's alive . love you's mwahh*

<3.maurajean'

where did i leave you off? i don't remember so i suppose i will tell you of this past week. monday was valentine's day* which was wonderful for the most part . hahaa- my past valentine's days have always had something gone terribly wrong so i was a little hesitant on whether or not to be happy about it - colleen brought me a rose and i felt oh-so-special so thank you for that my dear* for the majority of school it was pretty gay and my "best friend" seems to be confused as to "why i'm mad at her" and she feels the need to talk to every other person in the world about it except the only person it fucking concerns. WHATEVER I DONT CARE ANYMORE-- so i left after 6th because my mommy said i could. i walked out to my car spacing off as usual . when i had my key in the door i looked in and noticed a huggeee thing of pink roses were in my seat!!! i screamed because it scared me at first and then i almost cried because it was so sweet of my boyfriend <3* see initially we said no presents so i just got him a card a picture of us and some candy . you know little things - and he surprised me with that and i love him all the moreee! - i went home and got all pretty pretty and he came over and i gave him his little gift . we talked to my mommy for a bit and then left to go back to jay for my gay national honors society meeting shit . i thought it was going to be a quick one but after about 35 minutes renato got a phone call and walked out . lol and never came back -me and collz were laughing at that one - anywhoo so when it was over i went out to his car and he was a bit unhappy . he's been sick for a while and he gets tired easily- we had a nice little v-day to ourselves . we made dinner and watched movies and cuddled lots and lots . going out is to stressful and we had our own plans! *smiles* i got home around 11 i think and went to sleep because i was pooped! school tuesday wasnt too bad . hung out with renato again lol - wednesday i was supposed to work but dave switched with me . i feel like all week all i've been hearing about is prom and it's getting ridiculous - to the point where i feel like not going anymore and  i know everybody else has been feeling the same way- yea so today was my only day of work this week - hahaa ohh well .  i went up to renato's for a bit and we picked his brother up from school - he got his results back today and it turns out he has mono - ohh shit .. but he's at the end of it so i guess its not contagious - i didnt get it tho ?? strange . so i'm at work now bored out of my mind continuously putting off my book report for english - i better get my ass moving . leave a comment if you'd like - love you's *

<3.mj*

i know it's been a while - i just haven't updated cuz i haven't had the time lately but so here i am! february hasn't been so bad . i ordered springs for my car! yayy - i don't remember much of what i've done - most of my time is spent with school, work, and renato- i went to mt.snow last saturday and that was a lot of fun - i missed skiing i was gonna die without it. that night i went home and showered cuz i was quite soar . i went to renato's for a smidge . sunday i woke up and my parents weren't home because they went to rosco for the saturday-sunday . it was kind of wierd going to bed with nobody home . well kevin was but he doesn't count. anywhoo sunday feb.6th was my ashley's birthday!!! she's 17 - i love you ashiieee* me sara ash n danielle d. went to the diner . then we departed . i went home to change and then scooted up to wappingers . me and renato washed our cars and mine has a bunch of new scratches . thanks to my inconsiderate family . cool right? anywhoo this past week i've been an angry little beaver and lashed out on everybodyy-- i put a stop to it now . i'm better - today was a good day- i was so happy and i couldn't sit still at all in school . everybody was talking so much about prom and it was strange. idk what i'm gonna do about it - i don't want to make renato go with me if he doesnt want to.. i'll let him decide whether or not he wants to . so i left after 6th cuz i only had lunch and english which we don't do anything anyway . oh speaking of school i got my report card . overall was a 92 - dammmmnnn gooddd .. hahaa - me and collz handed in our little papers for the national honors society - woohoo i'm smart . i don't want to go to the meeting on monday cuz it's valentine's day and i would much rather spend that hour with my boyfriend cuddling for the day . we said no presents but i got him something and its cute . sentimental and i love it! -- anywhoo so i'm at work . i kinda wanted to go see a movie tonight 'cuz i feel like going out into the world but i don't know yet -- so here i am and i'll be back here tomorrow morning!!! i got alot of papers to do and some homework as well .. i'll write again soon - love you's*

<3.always - miss maura jean*

helloo there kiddies - it's been a while ehh? this week i have off due to the regents . thank god! its my first week off grounding too so this is time that is very much needed. i had 2 midterms this week . my math midterm was bullshit and my chem midterm was actually easier than i thought it would be . im a little nervous about how i did on them tho . i didn't study soOo you never know . anywhoo after the test today the kids went to denny's to eat . i think they were going to the mall after? but everybody complained of having no money . hahahaa i love itt - i went home to find that my mother did not go to work today . she made me angry. i went to renato's house . my lazy little bum was still in bed so i curled up next to him and he was nice and warm . *sighs* -- hahaa . so i hung out with him and we went to hand in an application for him . we ate a lot again today . were piglets - lol you only live once so what the hell? then i had to come to work - which sucks really bad because i'm NOT in the mood to be here and freeze my ass off . i don't have school tomorrow so i'm excited for that . maybe i'll go out tonight! thats all for now . love you's*

<3.maurajeanie*

so i'm still on house arrest. my past weekend was so boring i don't think i've EVER spent that much time in my room. i got some things done and i suppose this week i will finish my project for ceramics. i saw renato today after school that was much needed . i miss him so muchh!! oh well 4 more days until saturday- yay!! school wasn't so bad today; i ate a bagel this morning on the way to school AND shifted AND steered all on my own . i'm skilled - chem was good . we had a sub - i stayed awake in math for once and we reviewed- well needed . ceramics was okay . i started glazing my hugeee coil pot. me and sara went to the library for our gay research project . tomorrow i get my class ring! yayyy -- i'm excited. so after school i ran a red light because i hate waiting . it takes too long and i was in a rush - i saw my better half for a bit . we chatted and it was good to atleast see him. i went home and cleaned and did some homework and then i went to wendy's to meet him yet again . hahaa - we ate and talked with scotty there too . there was a lot of people there which was wierd . so then we walked to our cars and he stuck his head in to say goodbye and i grabbed him and pulled him in and almost kidnapped him. so im going to go start my papers . i'll write whenever - love you's*

<3.mj'

hey guys - it's been a while . if you don't already know i'm grounded for 2 weeks due to my retarded situation last saturday . january 22nd is my day of freedom! - it's not like i'm counting or anything [6 days left] -- i know now everything is going to be different. no trust with my parents. no sleepovers for a long ass while. as renato says i'll be "needing permission slips and a chaperone for everywhere i go" - haha it won't be that bad i swear. atleast i have school to see everybody, and work to go online. but i'm missing my love like crazyy<3** -- for the first time in a week i saw barcia and talked to her for more than 35 seconds. were both pretty much screwed . i didn't get to go to stratton this weekend so i'm pretty bummed about that. oh well it was no skiing or 1 more week. fuck that i need to get out of heree! - anywhoo all week nothing has happened that was special. [well maybe some things :)] i have 3 projects due and i just keep putting them off, my windshield wiper broke and i can't get this stupid piece off to look at what happened, i haven't talked to my dad- i've given up on it because it's useless we've never gotten along. as long as me and my mom are talking then i'm good. if your wondering why my mood doesnt exactly match my tone of writing thats because the only thing i have to be excited for is saturday! It's amazing that George Carlin, gross and mouthy comedian, could write something so very eloquent. A wonderful Message by George Carlin:

The paradox of our time in history is that we have taller buildings but shorter tempers, wider freeways, but narrower viewpoints. We spend more, but have less, we buy more, but enjoy less. We have bigger houses and smaller families, more conveniences, but less time. We have more degrees but less sense, more knowledge, but less judgment, more experts, yet more problems, more medicine, but less wellness. We drink too much, smoke too much, spend too recklessly, laugh too little, drive too fast, get too angry, stay up too late, get up too tired, read too little, watch TV too much, and pray too seldom. We have multiplied our possessions, but reduced our values. We talk too much, love too seldom, and hate too often. We've learned how to make a living, but not a life. We've added years to life, not life to years. We've been all the way to the moon and back, but have trouble crossing the street to meet a new neighbor. We conquered outer space but not inner space. We've done larger things, but not better things. We've cleaned up the air, but polluted the soul. We've conquered the atom, but not our prejudice. We write more, but learn less. We plan more, but accomplish less. We've learned to rush, but not to wait. We build more computers to hold more information, to produce more copies than ever, but we communicate less and less. These are the times of fast foods and slow digestion, big men and small character, steep profits and shallow relationships. These are the days of two incomes but more divorce, fancier houses, but broken homes. These are days of quick trips, disposable diapers, throwaway morality, one night stands, overweight bodies, and pills that do everything from cheer, to quiet, to kill. It is a time when there is much in the showroom window and nothing in the stockroom. A time when technology can bring this letter to you, and a time when you can choose either to share this insight, or to just hit delete. Remember, spend some time with your loved ones, because they are not going to be around forever. Remember, say a kind word to someone who looks up to you in awe, because that little person soon will grow up and leave your side. Remember, to give a warm hug to the one next to you, because that is the only treasure you can give with your heart and it doesn't cost a cent. Remember to say "I love you" to your partner and your loved ones, but most of all mean it. A kiss and an embrace will mend hurt when it comes from deep inside of you. Remember to hold hands and cherish the moment for someday that person will not be there. Give time to love, give time to speak, and give time to share the precious thoughts in your mind. AND ALWAYS REMEMBER: Life is not measured by the number of breaths we take, but by the moments that take our breath away.  >George Carlin
